== English ==

=== Noun ===

'''neologism''' (''plural:'' '''[[neologisms]]''')

# A word or phrase which has recently been coined; a new word or phrase. 
# The act or instance of coining, or uttering a new word. (e.g. "That dude seems like a Trupplelaufagain.")

